msgid "Scenario IV: Return to The Unspeakable Oath"
msgstr "冒险IV：重返邪秽誓约"

msgid "Set the following cards aside, out of play: Daniel Chesterfield, Host of Insanity, Radical Treatment, and each copy of Patient Confinement."
msgstr "将下列卡牌放在一边，位于场外：丹尼尔·契斯特菲尔德，疯狂之主敌人，根除疗法诡计以及所有的病人拘禁室。"

msgid "Because you have more (or equal) <b>Conviction</b> than <b>Doubt</b>, use Act 2—”The Really Bad Ones” (v. III)."
msgstr "因为你拥有的<b>确信</b>数多于(或等于)<b>疑惑</b>数，使用新的场景2——“真正可怕的人(版本三)”。"

msgid "Because you have more <b>Doubt</b> than <b>Conviction</b>, use Act 2—”The Really Bad Ones” (v. IV)."
msgstr "如果你拥有的<b>疑惑</b>数多于<b>确信</b>数，使用新的场景2——“真正可怕的人(版本四)”。"
